    <lb n="32"/>ἐπὶ <unclear>π</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ο</supplied><unclear>λλ</unclear>ῶν· ἀσ<unclear>πά</unclear>ζ<unclear>ο</unclear>μαι κατʼ ὄνομα 

